title: CCK Podcast: Draft Day
description:
All the awkward moments from NFL draftee's living rooms. Who would be in your draft party? Do college girlfriends make the cut? That's Right, Zah t-shirts on the way. The Becton family is absolutely massive.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kfcr
